    "description": "Ever wanted to just chill and watch videos with your friends at the same time without the need of screensharing?<br><br>Introducing Movie Night a casual online multiplayer game allowing players to create their own virtual private cinema. Movie Night is and will always be free to play with absolutely <strong>NO microtransactions, paid DLC, or subscriptions.</strong> Create a room with up to 16 players with full control over what is played on your cinema screen with just a youtube URL.<br><br>Once a player creates their own game they can choose from a range of different maps to set the scene. All players in the same game can request videos and enjoy watching together in realtime.<br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> XP level system<br></li><li> Steam Achievements<br></li><li> Watch videos in HD together in realtime<br></li><li> Multiple Maps<br></li><li> Customise your own avatar and clothing<br></li><li> Lightweight and can run on lower end machines</li></ul>",
